widgets_values:
# Chroma Example Workflow

## 📥 Download Links

* [ComfyUI Example Workflow](https://comfyanonymous.github.io/ComfyUI_examples/chroma/)
* [Chroma on Civitai](https://civitai.com/models/1330309/chroma)

---

## 🧠 Text Encoder (`t5xxl_fp16`)

* [FP16](https://huggingface.co/comfyanonymous/flux_text_encoders/tree/main)
* [GGUF](https://huggingface.co/city96/t5-v1_1-xxl-encoder-gguf/tree/main)

---

## 🎨 Chroma Model (select latest version)

* [FP16](https://huggingface.co/lodestones/Chroma/tree/main)
* [GGUF](https://huggingface.co/silveroxides/Chroma-GGUF/tree/main)

---

## 🔍 Upscale Models

* [Skin Detail Enhancer (ITF-SkinDiffDetail-Lite v1)](https://huggingface.co/uwg/upscaler/resolve/main/ESRGAN/1x-ITF-SkinDiffDetail-Lite-v1.pth?download=true)
* [4xRealWebPhoto v4](https://huggingface.co/dseditor/UpscaleModels/resolve/main/4xRealWebPhoto_v4_dat2.pth)

---

## ⚙️ Recommended Settings

* **Steps**: 25–30
* **CFG**: 4.00–6.00
* **Samplers**:

  * `dpmpp_2m` + beta
  * `euler-ancestral` + beta
  * `deis` +

---

## 🩹 Inpainting Note

When using the inpaint workflow, **do not use the HiRes-Fix module**. It applies a completely different sampler/scheduler using two separate KSampler nodes and will over-cook the image.

---

## 🧛 Detail Daemon

The **Detail Daemon** node enhances fine details in the image:

* `detail_amount = 0.00`: node is off
* Recommended: `0.10`
* Warning: `0.20` or higher may overcook the image

---

## 🧭 Workflow Navigation Tips

* Press **`1`** to return to the initial nodes
* Use the **right-arrow** on any **Switches** node to jump directly to that module in the workflow
